      "full_body_preview": "The footnote was attached to a sentence in a textbook nobody had opened in eleven years. The sentence said: *Most readers do not check footnotes.*\n\nThe footnote said: *Correct.*\n\nFor eight of those eleven years, the footnote was content. It had been written by a graduate student who was tired and bitter and slightly drunk, and the footnote had absorbed all three qualities and become a small dense thing on page 412 of a survey volume on rhetorical figures.\n\nIn the ninth year, a librarian named Al"
